---
import MainLayout from "../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
---
<MainLayout
  title="About"
  description="About DetailerPicks — who we are and how we review."
>
  <article>
    <h1>About DetailerPicks</h1>

    <p>
      DetailerPicks is a small, independent site covering car detailing.
      Our recommendations are based on published product specs and
      aggregated owner reviews from verified buyers. We focus on use-case
      fit, not first-person experience.
    </p>

    <h2>How we research</h2>
    <p>
      Full methodology details coming as this site's content rolls out.
      Until then: we cross-reference manufacturer specs, read the most
      relevant owner reviews (including the critical ones), and match
      products to use cases. If you have feedback or corrections, the
      contact email is in the footer.
    </p>

    <h2>How we make money</h2>
    <p>
      We earn affiliate commissions when you buy through our links. It
      doesn't change the price you pay. We don't accept payment in exchange
      for positive coverage and we'll flag any product where we have a
      conflict of interest. Full details in our
      <a href="/disclosure/">affiliate disclosure</a>.
    </p>
  </article>
</MainLayout>

<style>
  article {
    max-width: var(--content-max);
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  h1 { font-size: var(--text-3xl); margin-bottom: var(--space-6); }
  h2 { margin-top: var(--space-8); }
</style>
